{"tid":1750763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果過300萬票我就維園裸跑！快啲叫人投啦！","createTime":"2019-11-24T13:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T00:08:14.000Z","uid":26018,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3131e2e6f0d14f83d8cb6ffe86e1f923983852","tid":1750763,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕不走數"},{"pid":"7c2ef86e955d2695db604acb29f8c488862b0cc2","tid":1750763,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:36:48.000Z","msg":"26/11 全城樂手齊心演奏薈通利<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1748620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1748620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n黃店與藍店之間總有綠店，不表態、裝作中立。 我們沒有必要跟中共一樣，迫每間公司歸邊。既然深藍老闆要扮作政治中立，就不要以為滅聲、不談政治就是中立，事實是容不下員工的反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n平日琴行歡迎客人、甚至員工試玩樂器，既然琴行要賺黃絲Band 仔的錢，就不應該對他們彈奏《願榮光歸香港》不滿。如不歡迎黃絲客人，罵他們做「曱甴」，不如叫手足直接將琴行加盟藍店。<br />\n<br />\n用音樂感化「偽綠店」，號召各樂手一同到琴行試玩樂器，齊齊演奏《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n不會樂器的朋友歡迎一起詠唱或當樂迷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全城樂手齊心演奏薈通利<br />\n日期：2019年11月26日（星期二）<br />\n時間：7:30pm<br />\n地點：尖沙咀通利琴行<br />\n衣著：做返自己 （宜戴口罩防二噁英）<br />\n大會指定歌曲：《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n結他譜下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guitarians.com/chord/76287/香港人-願榮光歸香港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guitarians.com%2Fchord%2F76287%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=e15ea69e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guitarians.com/chord/76287/香港人-願榮光歸香港</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MwV9Jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MwV9Jf.jpg&h=68035d32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fbea2b88d255debe30d7bf5ae7f618cee62bba0","tid":1750763,"uid":192893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"同燒山對燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312b206aa5fdda7704030ab35546825de0b2dd9b","tid":1750763,"uid":192893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"留名睇找數"},{"pid":"7113f367c4924a1070c418b260e505e7979be4d0","tid":1750763,"uid":192893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"唔好令我失望"},{"pid":"7869c5f29c68ed3f33eb59a612aea6fade212ddc","tid":1750763,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d56c8a291c7dab5b515907d60e43113cd21b2ad","tid":1750763,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"留名等找數"},{"pid":"457a9441467aeabfd8c3795d30acc84771283f5f","tid":1750763,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ig直播裸跑</span>"},{"pid":"20d0f5fc3b63fe2c089352525259811069f5ba81","tid":1750763,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T1